434
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:43,090
Nadace Jumenokata?

435
00:21:43,130 --> 00:21:44,880
Ten proslulý projekt rozvoje města?

436
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:45,590
Ano.

437
00:21:45,630 --> 00:21:46,970
Vlastně...

438
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:52,970
